DIGEST / LOCAL NEWS IN BRIEF: DRIVER CHARGED IN TRUCK CRASH FATALITY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A Canoga Park man was killed and a companion was charged in his death Saturday 
