</P>
<P>
Favor constitutional amendment to prohibit burning the American flag? yes 
</P>
<P>
Support woman's right to abortion on demand? no 
</P>
<P>
Should public funds be used for abortions for poor women? no 
</P>
<P>
Ban on sale of assault rifles? no 
</P>
<P>
Top 3 spending priorities: crime-drugs, transportation, health care 
</P>
<P>
Most important issue in distict: quality of life 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Candidate: Tricia Hunter 
</P>
<P>
